imdb.plot outline: Ben's Menu is an exciting foodie series hosted by Masterchef favourite, Ben Milbourne. Filmed at Ben's picturesque farmhouse in northwest Tasmania, Ben's Menu unearths Australia's best produce to create dishes that'll make your mouth water. Ben cooks with friends and family, shares his most cherished recipes, and all the cooking tips he's picked up on his journey from high school teacher to acclaimed cook.
